The program 'jmirror' is designed to mirror an entire FTP site
or directory.  This is REALLY useful for people who use an ftp
client that cannot download recursively.  This requires both
PERL 5 (/usr/ports/lang/perl5/), and the CPAN module Net:FTP 
(http://www.perl.org/CPAN/).

WWW: http://jmirror.ruin.org/

- Justin Robinson
jmrobins@jmirror.ruin.org
